    {
      "title": "COMMITEE Protocols\nEnclave Verification Protocol\nP_i verifying the Enclave\n1. Send the message (Verify_enclave) to O\nO upon (Verify_enclave) from P_i\n2. Send the message (mpk, pk_E, \\sigma, \\rho) to P_i\nP_i upon (mpk, pk_E, \\sigma, \\rho) from O\n3. Abort if VrfyQuote(mpk, p_{CT}(\\kappa), (pk_E, \\sigma), \\rho) \\neq 1\nor\nVrfy(mpk, pk_E, \\sigma) \\neq 1 or \\Gamma.pk_{TEE} \\neq pk_E\nDeposit Phase Protocol\nP_i depositing v_i coins\n1. Send (deposit, pk_i, v_i) to \\Gamma\nO at the end of deposit phase\n2. Let \\bar{\\mathbf{b}} := \\mathbf{b}. get(t+k)\n3. (\\mathcal{D}_{\\Gamma}, \\sigma_E) \\leftarrow \\mathsf{E.DEPOSIT}(\\mathbf{b})\n4. Send (\\mathcal{D}_{\\Gamma}, \\sigma_E) to all parties enlisted in \\mathcal{D}_{\\Gamma}\nP_i at the end of the deposit phase",
